items.title: India to probe fire at Tata plant making components for Apple iPhones
items.description: The incident is the latest in recent years to affect Apple suppliers in India, where the US firm is diversifying its supply chain beyond China and which it sees as a growth market

items.title: L&T Semicon expects its chip production to start in 2 years; to set up unit later
items.description: The scope of this work could include processor design for edge devices and hybrid cloud systems, as well as for areas like mobility, industrial, energy, and servers.
